<L>__{interior tom's apartment night}
<A>__{a car door slams in the street below he goes towards the window which is blocked by his sofa puts his knees in and looks out. tom's p.o.v. a woman walking from a car.}
<B>__{on tom}
<A>__{momentarily thinking it's jane. elated. tom's p.o.v. it is not jane. the phone rings.}
<L>__{intercut:}
<B>__{back to scene}
<A>__{as he answers and we have the following conversation between jane, who is using the phone, with aaron seen just a few feet away. tom in his apartment.}
<C>__{jane}
<D>__{hi. it's me.}
<C>__{tom}
<D>__{where are you?}
