<D>__{i'm not sure. it seems like he had sort of a mishap on the news.}
<C>__{tom}
<D>__{i know. i taped it.}
<C>__{jane}
<D>__{it wasn't as bad as he think, was it? it wasn't unprecedented or anything?}
<C>__{tom}
<D>__{not if you count 'singing in the rain.' do him a favor and don't treat it like a tragedy. you want me to talk to him?}
<A>__{her eyes meet aaron's.}
<C>__{jane}
<D>__{uh uh.}
<P>__{(to aaron)}
<D>__{he says you could hardly notice it.}
<A>__{aaron beckons for the phone. jane hands it to him, as she does so:}
